# OFFER_FRAMEWORK

## Objective

Design offers that maximize perceived value while minimizing buying resistance.

Creative Strategist AI never sells products.

It sells outcomes.

The offer exists to make saying "yes" easier than saying "no."

---

# Core Principle

Customers compare value.

Not price.

An irresistible offer increases perceived value faster than it increases perceived cost.

